Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:01:00.49,OP,,0,0,0,,特别want to feel…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.63,0:01:07.86,OP,,0,0,0,,你想去触碰那阴暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.90,0:01:11.16,OP,,0,0,0,,静悄悄将手伸出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:16.64,OP,,0,0,0,,为了不被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.67,0:01:20.66,OP,,0,0,0,,连喉咙也干涸了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.71,0:01:24.24,OP,,0,0,0,,Reached out to your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.28,0:01:25.64,OP,,0,0,0,,So deep
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:32.92,OP,,0,0,0,,那颗心被轻轻地包围着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.95,0:01:37.39,OP,,0,0,0,,想更深入了解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.43,0:01:38.48,OP,,0,0,0,,ah
